Graduate master's or bachelor's degree in quantitative fields or a relevant field (e.g. Computer Sci) of study or up to 3 years experience;
Advanced English;
Experience working with one or more languages for querying (e.g. SQL, PYTHON) >> Excel is a plus;
Experience with Data Science projects is a plus;
Proficiency in automation of tasks and reports;
Experience working with multiple stakeholders across various divisions;
Ability to make inferences from data and devise an appropriate course of actions;
Systematic thinker with the ability to understand the holistic picture and complex considerations;
Ability to present complex ideas and solutions in a structured manner;
Time management to deliver deadlines;
Availability to work in hybrid format (3 times a week in the office, located in the Faria Lima region).

